caption: #contest it would be really really cool to meet jack and Jack by winning this concert. I've had a fan account on Instagram ( @datewithjack ) for over a year now and Jack and Jack have been my idols for even longer than that and I haven't actually gotten a chance to meet them. I went to digi tour Chicago last August and I think it's safe to say that that was the greatest day of my life. They've come so far and I would do anything to meet them :))
